<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0216001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0216001">「一背闍」，底本為 ekapecchaṁ，脚註異本為 ekaṁ pacchaṁ暹羅本為 ekaṁ veccaṁ。究為何物不明，概為一種坐或乘用之具。</note>
<note n="0218001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218001">「輕烤糖果」，底本為 lahupūpapavaṁ，脚註所示異本為 labhusupuṭakaṁ，又暹羅本為 supatikaṁ，以上均不明了，今暫假字讀為 lahupūpapakkaṁ（SK, Pakvaṁ）。</note>
<note n="0222001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0222001">「望求榮達」，底本為 vuṭṭhikāmā，今採用暹羅本之 vuddhikāmā。</note>
<note n="0222002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0222002">「於我皆享有……此亦常於有」，底本為 bhavesaṁ sabbato bhave，今採暹羅本之 bhave'haṁ sabbadā bhave。</note>
<note n="0224001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0224001">「我有物甚多」，底本為 pahū tadā，今採用暹羅本之 pahū mamaṁ。</note>
<note n="0226002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226002">「勝者究諦、智」，底本為 saccaneyyantago jino 應讀為 saccañe yyantago jino。</note>
<note n="0226003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226003">「如勝太陽」，底本為 sattasāravare tasmim，今採用暹羅本之 sataraṁsivare tasmiṁ。</note>
<note n="0226004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226004">「有大利」，底本為 mahiddhikā，（有大神力）今採用暹羅本之 mahātthikā。</note>
<note n="0226005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226005">「僧伽聽我言」，底本為 rasaddhovisamāyuto，文意不明，今採用暹羅本之 saṅghovirasamāsuto。</note>
<note n="0227006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0227006">「敬愛我度日」，底本為 divasa-saṅko'haṁ，又暹羅本為 saradīva sasanko'ham，兩者皆難判讀正確，今暫假讀為 diva-saṅkamanto。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
